CRD and Custom Controller

Architecture Looks something like this:
https://github.com/kubernetes/sample-controller/blob/master/docs/controller-client-go.mdï¿¼

Best Reference:
https://github.com/kubernetes/sample-controller

kubectl get customresourcedefinition
NAME                           CREATED AT
foos.samplecontroller.k8s.io   2019-02-08T09:34:12Z

kubectl edit customresourcedefinition foos.samplecontroller.k8s.io
apiVersion: apiextensions.k8s.io/v1beta1
kind: CustomResourceDefinition
metadata:
  creationTimestamp: "2019-02-08T09:34:12Z"
  generation: 1
  name: foos.samplecontroller.k8s.io
  resourceVersion: "14704"
  selfLink: /apis/apiextensions.k8s.io/v1beta1/customresourcedefinitions/foos.samplecontroller.k8s.io
  uid: b18c63e7-2b84-11e9-82d4-080027e3eac4
spec:
  group: samplecontroller.k8s.io
  names:
    kind: Foo
    listKind: FooList
    plural: foos
    singular: foo
  scope: Namespaced
  version: v1alpha1
status:
  acceptedNames:
    kind: Foo
    listKind: FooList
    plural: foos
    singular: foo
  conditions:
  - lastTransitionTime: "2019-02-08T09:34:12Z"
    message: no conflicts found
    reason: NoConflicts
    status: "True"
    type: NamesAccepted
  - lastTransitionTime: "2019-02-08T09:34:12Z"
    message: the initial names have been accepted
    reason: InitialNamesAccepted
    status: "True"
    type: Established

Custom Resource Object

kubectl get foo
NAME          CREATED AT
example-foo   1h

kubectl edit foo example-foo
apiVersion: samplecontroller.k8s.io/v1alpha1
kind: Foo
metadata:
  clusterName: ""
  creationTimestamp: "2019-02-08T09:34:21Z"
  generation: 1
  name: example-foo
  namespace: default
  resourceVersion: "15765"
  selfLink: /apis/samplecontroller.k8s.io/v1alpha1/namespaces/default/foos/example-foo
  uid: b6a8861b-2b84-11e9-82d4-080027e3eac4
spec:
  deploymentName: example-foo
  replicas: 1
status:
  availableReplicas: 1


Custom Controller

kubectl get deployment
NAME          DESIRED   CURRENT   UP-TO-DATE   AVAILABLE   AGE
example-foo   1         1         1            1           1h

kubectl edit deployment 
apiVersion: extensions/v1beta1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  annotations:
    deployment.kubernetes.io/revision: "1"
  creationTimestamp: "2019-02-08T09:49:34Z"
  generation: 1
  name: example-foo
  namespace: default
  ownerReferences:
  - apiVersion: samplecontroller.k8s.io/v1alpha1
    blockOwnerDeletion: true
    controller: true
    kind: Foo
    name: example-foo
    uid: b6a8861b-2b84-11e9-82d4-080027e3eac4
  resourceVersion: "15764"
  selfLink: /apis/extensions/v1beta1/namespaces/default/deployments/example-foo
  uid: d7331f42-2b86-11e9-82d4-080027e3eac4
spec:
  progressDeadlineSeconds: 600
  replicas: 1
  revisionHistoryLimit: 10
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: nginx
      controller: example-foo
  strategy:
    rollingUpdate:
      maxSurge: 25%
      maxUnavailable: 25%
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      creationTimestamp: null
      labels:
        app: nginx
        controller: example-foo
    spec:
      containers:
      - image: nginx:latest
        imagePullPolicy: Always
        name: nginx
        resources: {}
        terminationMessagePath: /dev/termination-log
        terminationMessagePolicy: File
      dnsPolicy: ClusterFirst
      restartPolicy: Always
      schedulerName: default-scheduler
      securityContext: {}
      terminationGracePeriodSeconds: 30

Validating a CRD (This is needed to restrict user from creating a invalid configuration)
apiVersion: apiextensions.k8s.io/v1beta1
kind: CustomResourceDefinition
metadata:
  name: crontabs.stable.example.com
spec:
  group: stable.example.com
  versions:
    - name: v1
      served: true
      storage: true
  version: v1
  scope: Namespaced
  names:
    plural: crontabs
    singular: crontab
    kind: CronTab
    shortNames:
    - ct
  validation:
   # openAPIV3Schema is the schema for validating custom objects.
    openAPIV3Schema:
      properties:
        spec:
          properties:
            cronSpec:
              type: string
              pattern: '^(\d+|\*)(/\d+)?(\s+(\d+|\*)(/\d+)?){4}$'
            replicas:
              type: integer
              minimum: 1
              maximum: 10





